{"fadein":1.5,"fadeType":1,"id":"FUYINGYINGHUA19","continueBgm":true,"mode":2,"once":true,"scripts":[{"side":2,"bgm":"xinnong-2","say":"In a sea surrounded by darkness, two girls were trying to make their escape.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"say":"Kawakaze!","nameColor":"#a9f548","flashN":{"color":[1,1,1],"alpha":[[0,1,0.2],[1,0,0.2,0.2],[0,1,0.2,0.4],[1,0,0.2,0.6]]},"dir":1,"soundeffect":"event:\/battle\/boom2","actor":305050},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"Shells from Siren battleships rained down ceaselessly around Kawakaze.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Lady Nagato, please stand back! I shall deal with this!","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":301490},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"What are you saying?! Your equipment is already in tatters!","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":305050},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Falling into the Sirens' trap and endangering Lady Nagato is an unforgivable sin...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":301490},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Allow me to atone for my transgressions with my life!","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":301490},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"The thunderous roar of a cannon was followed by an explosion...","flashN":{"color":[1,1,1],"alpha":[[0,1,0.2],[1,0,0.2,0.2],[0,1,0.2,0.4],[1,0,0.2,0.6]]},"dir":1,"soundeffect":"event:\/battle\/boom2","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"But when the smoke cleared, it was a mass-produced Sakura battleship that lay in ruins, not Kawakaze.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Lady Nagato, why would you expend your power to protect me...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":301490},{"side":2,"say":"What are you saying, you fool!","action":[{"number":2,"x":0,"type":"shake","delay":0,"dur":0.15,"y":30}],"nameColor":"#a9f548","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":305050},{"side":2,"say":"Lady Nagato?","action":[{"number":2,"x":20,"type":"shake","delay":0,"dur":0.15,"y":0}],"nameColor":"#a9f548","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":301490},{"side":2,"say":"I am Nagato, Nagato of the Sakura Empire!","action":[{"number":2,"x":0,"type":"shake","delay":0,"dur":0.15,"y":30}],"nameColor":"#a9f548","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":305050},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"If I cannot protect even a single comrade, how am I to protect the Sakura Empire?","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":305050},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Lady... Nagato...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":301490},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"Having failed to secure the kill, the Siren battleship's movements stopped briefly. Seizing upon that moment...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Witness the power of the Big Seven!","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":305050},{"flashN":{"color":[1,1,1],"alpha":[[0,1,0.2],[1,0,0.2,0.2],[0,1,0.2,0.4],[1,0,0.2,0.6]]},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"soundeffect":"event:\/battle\/boom2","say":"BOOOM!!!"},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"The massive guns that bore the weight of protecting a nation rang out. Such power tore apart the enemy with ease.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"In an instant, the enemy forces were engulfed in a sea of fire, and the Siren siege began to fall apart.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Lady Nagato, your power...!","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":301490},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Kawakaze!!","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":305050},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"Nagato extended her hand to the injured Kawakaze, half towing her towards their escape route.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"...However, the enemies began to close in on the encumbered Nagato once more.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Lady Nagato, please put me down! You must make it out!","dir":1,"soundeffect":"event:\/battle\/boom2","actor":301490},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"Ignoring Kawakaze's protests, Nagato raised her formidable rigging, firing back at the encroaching enemies while doing her best to avoid their barrage.","dir":1,"soundeffect":"event:\/battle\/boom2","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"As Nagato tried to carve out an escape route with her attacks, more Sirens quickly arose to take the place of the fallen.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Lady Nagato!","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":301490},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"Kawakaze broke free from Nagato and used the last of her power to charge forward.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"The Sakura Empire needs you... Lady Nagato, you must live on...!","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":301490},{"bgm":"story-7","say":"——","flashN":{"color":[1,1,1],"alpha":[[0,1,0.2],[1,0,0.2,0.2],[0,1,0.2,0.4],[1,0,0.2,0.6]]},"soundeffect":"event:\/battle\/plane","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05}},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"Suddenly, several bombs rained down upon the approaching Siren forces.","flashN":{"color":[1,1,1],"alpha":[[0,1,0.2],[1,0,0.2,0.2],[0,1,0.2,0.4],[1,0,0.2,0.6]]},"dir":1,"soundeffect":"event:\/battle\/boom2","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"While your spirit is commendable, you mustn't follow through with that!","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":307060},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"say":"Do you know how sad Nagato would be if she lost you?!","nameColor":"#a9f548","flashN":{"color":[1,1,1],"alpha":[[0,1,0.2],[1,0,0.2,0.2],[0,1,0.2,0.4],[1,0,0.2,0.6]]},"dir":1,"soundeffect":"event:\/battle\/boom2","actor":307060},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"The night sky glowed brightly with explosions from Zuikaku's dive bombers, which brought an end to their crisis.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"black":true,"delay":0.5,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[1,0]},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"action":[{"x":0,"type":"move","delay":1.5,"dur":0.25,"y":-1250}],"nameColor":"#a9f548","flashout":{"black":true,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[0,1]},"dir":1,"say":"Zuikaku... I am in your debt...","actor":301490},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"In a mix of exhaustion and relief, Kawakaze fell into Zuikaku's bosom.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Kawakaze!","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":305050},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Don't worry. She's just overwhelmed from having strained herself.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":307060},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"You can rest now. That's a good girl.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":307060},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"You saved me once again... Thank you, Zuikaku.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":305050},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Ah, um, I just happened to be passing by!","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":307060},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"R-really?","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":305050},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Yeah, I was just leaving the banquet when these Sirens suddenly showed up, so I thought I'd go teach them a lesson.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":307060},{"side":2,"action":[{"number":2,"x":20,"type":"shake","delay":0,"dur":0.3,"y":0}],"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Lady Nagato...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":301490},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"If the Sirens are here, they must be after Watatsumi...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":301490},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"There's no reason for you to go out of your way to take such a big risk...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":301490},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"I disagree. I should be the one to conduct this ritual.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":305050},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"More importantly, if the Sirens truly are after Watatsumi, we must never let their plans come to fruition.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":305050},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Zuikaku, can I leave Kawakaze with you? She needs to rest.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":305050},{"side":2,"say":"Of course! Lady Nagato, Mikasa is waiting for you on the island!","action":[{"number":2,"x":0,"type":"shake","delay":0,"dur":0.15,"y":30}],"nameColor":"#a9f548","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":307060}]}